 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}^{m}(k)$
\end_inset

 with homogeneous coordinates 
\begin_inset Formula $Y_{0},\dots,Y_{m}$
\end_inset

.
 We want to find an easy description of the product 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}^{n}(k)\times\mathbb{P}^{m}(k)$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

